    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "depth": 4,
      "title": "（2）資料規模與模型選擇",
      "anchor": "2資料規模與模型選擇",
      "pageIndex": 146,
      "bbox": [
        70.24,
        525.91,
        218.23,
        539.2
      ],
      "id": "block-55",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "heading",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 5,
      "text": "資料量不僅影響模型訓練的可行性，更牽動模型選擇的策略方向。不同資料規模下，模型在表現力、穩定性與訓練效率之間需做出平衡。",
      "pageIndex": 146,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        551.95,
        517.93,
        589.12
      ],
      "indentFirstLine": false,
      "id": "block-56",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "小型資料集（數百至數千筆樣本）",
      "pageIndex": 146,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        600.75,
        311.23,
        614.2
      ],
      "id": "block-57",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "當樣本有限時，選擇結構簡單、參數數量少的模型能有效降低過擬合風險。例如線性迴歸、邏輯迴歸、決策樹或正則化模型（如 Lasso、Ridge） 為常見選項。",
      "pageIndex": 146,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        625.74,
        524.64,
        689.23
      ],
      "id": "block-58",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "此時資料前處理與特徵工程的重要性提高，需以較強的先驗假設支撐模型效果。",
      "pageIndex": 146,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        700.74,
        517.85,
        755.82
      ],
      "id": "block-59",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "中型資料集（數千至數十萬筆樣本）",
      "pageIndex": 147,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        100.66,
        323.85,
        114.11
      ],
      "id": "block-60",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "此區間提供模型一定的學習能力與泛化基礎，能夠支持較高表現力的模型如隨機森林、梯度提升機（XGBoost、LightGBM）等。",
      "pageIndex": 147,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        125.62,
        517.85,
        164.15
      ],
      "id": "block-61",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "可進一步嘗試模型集成與超參數優化，提升預測效能。同時，計算資源與訓練時間，會成為實務上必須考量的限制因素。",
      "pageIndex": 147,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        175.66,
        518.2,
        214.07
      ],
      "id": "block-62",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "大型資料集（百萬級以上樣本）",
      "pageIndex": 147,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        225.7,
        298.63,
        239.15
      ],
      "id": "block-63",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "大規模資料能發揮深度模型的表現潛力，特別是在非結構化資料（如影像、語音、文字）處理上，深度神經網路成為主要選擇。",
      "pageIndex": 147,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        250.69,
        518.23,
        289.1
      ],
      "id": "block-64",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "大型資料訓練也對運算能力、分散式架構支援、模型調校效率有更高要求。此時應選擇具擴展性且可配合GPU/多機訓練的架構設計。",
      "pageIndex": 147,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        300.73,
        518.2,
        339.14
      ],
      "id": "block-65",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "depth": 4,
      "title": "（3）模型解釋性需求",
      "anchor": "3模型解釋性需求",
      "pageIndex": 147,
      "bbox": [
        70.24,
        375.89,
        193.03,
        389.18
      ],
      "id": "block-66",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "heading",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 5,
      "text": "模型的可解釋性決定了其在特定領域的適用性，特別是在醫療、金融、法遵等需追溯模型決策邏輯的情境下，更是不可或缺。",
      "pageIndex": 147,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        401.93,
        517.93,
        439.1
      ],
      "indentFirstLine": false,
      "id": "block-67",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "高解釋性模型",
      "pageIndex": 147,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        450.75,
        197.83,
        464.2
      ],
      "id": "block-68",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "線性迴歸（Linear Regression）、邏輯迴歸（Logistic Regression）與淺層決策樹（Shallow Decision Tree）等模型具備結構簡單、邏輯可視化的特性。其決策過程明確，變數對預測結果的影響可透過係數、分割規則等方式直接解釋，便於使用者進行結果溝通與審查。",
      "pageIndex": 147,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        475.71,
        518.37,
        564.16
      ],
      "id": "block-69",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "此類模型常被應用於對可解釋性有明確要求的場域，如醫療診斷、信貸評分與法規監管等情境。",
      "pageIndex": 147,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        575.67,
        518.32,
        614.2
      ],
      "id": "block-70",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "低解釋性模型",
      "pageIndex": 147,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        625.74,
        197.83,
        639.19
      ],
      "id": "block-71",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "隨機森林（Random Forest）、梯度提升樹（Gradient Boosting Trees）與深度神經網路（Deep Neural Networks）等模型雖具備高度預測能力，但其結構高度非線性且包含大量參數，使得模型的決策過程不易直觀理解。",
      "pageIndex": 147,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        650.7,
        518.4,
        739.15
      ],
      "id": "block-72",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "在醫療、金融或法規敏感等高風險應用場景中，建議搭配模型可解釋性技術使用，例如SHAP（SHapley Additive exPlanations）、LIME（Local Interpretable Model-Agnostic Explanations）或偏依圖（Partial Dependence Plot），以輔助理解模型對特徵的依賴關係與輸出邏輯，進而提升模型透明度與可信度。",
      "pageIndex": 148,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        100.66,
        521.82,
        214.07
      ],
      "id": "block-73",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "depth": 4,
      "title": "（4）運算資源與實務部署限制",
      "anchor": "4運算資源與實務部署限制",
      "pageIndex": 148,
      "bbox": [
        70.24,
        250.85,
        243.43,
        264.14
      ],
      "id": "block-74",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "heading",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 5,
      "text": "實務應用中，模型部署往往受限於資源環境與即時反應需求。選擇模型時，除理論效能外，也應考量部署現實與維運成本。",
      "pageIndex": 148,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        276.89,
        518.23,
        314.18
      ],
      "indentFirstLine": false,
      "id": "block-75",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "資源受限場景（如IoT、手機App、邊緣裝置）",
      "pageIndex": 148,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        325.69,
        382.53,
        339.14
      ],
      "id": "block-76",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "適合選用模型結構簡單、參數少、推論快速的演算法，例如簡單決策樹、邏輯迴歸或經壓縮後的小型神經網路。亦可採用模型剪枝或量化等技術進行模型瘦身。",
      "pageIndex": 148,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        350.65,
        521.32,
        414.14
      ],
      "id": "block-77",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "資源充足場景（如雲端部署、資料中心）",
      "pageIndex": 148,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        425.65,
        349.05,
        439.1
      ],
      "id": "block-78",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "可使用高效能深度模型、模型集成策略，充分發揮硬體計算能力。同時能支援較複雜的資料前處理與後處理流程。",
      "pageIndex": 148,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        450.75,
        518.2,
        489.16
      ],
      "id": "block-79",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "即時推論需求",
      "pageIndex": 148,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        500.67,
        197.83,
        514.12
      ],
      "id": "block-80",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "在必須秒級或毫秒級回應的任務中（如金融交易、推薦系統），須優先考量模型的推論延遲與效能表現。可搭配caching、模型蒸餾（knowledge distillation）等技術提升即時表現。",
      "pageIndex": 148,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        525.75,
        521.77,
        589.12
      ],
      "id": "block-81",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 5,
      "text": "模型選擇與部署應同步規劃，避免訓練完成後才發現模型無法實際上線執行。",
      "pageIndex": 148,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        609.07,
        521.88,
        638.95
      ],
      "indentFirstLine": false,
      "id": "block-82",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "depth": 4,
      "title": "（5）偏差-變異的權衡（Bias-Variance Tradeoff）",
      "anchor": "5偏差-變異的權衡bias-variancetradeoff",
      "pageIndex": 149,
      "bbox": [
        70.24,
        100.82,
        347.97,
        114.11
      ],
      "id": "block-83",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "heading",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 5,
      "text": "模型選擇的核心原則之一是權衡偏差（bias）與變異（variance），兩者之間存在固有的取捨關係：",
      "pageIndex": 149,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        402.65,
        518.2,
        440.9
      ],
      "indentFirstLine": false,
      "id": "block-84",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "偏差（Bias）：",
      "pageIndex": 149,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        452.43,
        201.43,
        465.88
      ],
      "id": "block-85",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "指模型對資料結構的擬合能力不足，無法有效捕捉資料中的主要趨勢，導致系統性誤差偏高（欠擬合）。",
      "pageIndex": 149,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        477.51,
        521.44,
        515.92
      ],
      "id": "block-86",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "變異（Variance）：",
      "pageIndex": 149,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        527.43,
        223.27,
        540.88
      ],
      "id": "block-87",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "指模型對訓練資料的細微差異或雜訊過於敏感，導致模型在不同資料集上的表現差異大、泛化能力差（過擬合）。",
      "pageIndex": 149,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        552.51,
        517.85,
        590.92
      ],
      "id": "block-88",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 5,
      "text": "模型複雜度的提升通常伴隨偏差的降低與變異的提高，因此模型選擇應在二者之間取得適當平衡：",
      "pageIndex": 149,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        611.83,
        517.93,
        649.15
      ],
      "indentFirstLine": false,
      "id": "block-89",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "低複雜度模型（如線性迴歸）：",
      "pageIndex": 149,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        660.66,
        292.39,
        674.11
      ],
      "id": "block-90",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "偏差較高、變異較低，穩定且具解釋性，但無法處理複雜關係。",
      "pageIndex": 149,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        685.62,
        492.0,
        699.07
      ],
      "id": "block-91",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "高複雜度模型（如深度神經網路）：",
      "pageIndex": 149,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        710.7,
        317.59,
        724.15
      ],
      "id": "block-92",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "偏差低、變異高，可擬合複雜模式，但需更多資料或額外的正則化方法以控制變異。",
      "pageIndex": 149,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        735.66,
        517.91,
        774.06
      ],
      "id": "block-93",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c8",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    }
  ],
